PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 69 - which (a) declares that the flooding in August 2003 that affected several municipalities located on the south shore of the St. Lawrence River in the Province of QUEBEC, to be of concern to the federal government; and (b) authorizes the provision of financial assistance in that regard.
